desc_short	-----								XNemesis Sandbox is a 2D shooter SandBox game, it is a package that contains fully featured levels, Level Designer Software that allows you to create/modify levels and Assets Pack(s) as ready Templates to use in your levels if you don't have/want to use your own images/animations.							
developer									XProd Games								
